Alembic migrations for the IoTAPS backend.

Run from the `app/` directory:

  alembic upgrade head      # apply all migrations
  alembic downgrade -1      # roll back one revision
  alembic revision --autogenerate -m "message"   # generate a new migration

The database URL is taken from the DATABASE_URL environment variable; the
migration environment coerces it to the psycopg2 (sync) driver automatically.
